<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.10.6">
<l>vāṇeṭuṅkaṇ malarkkūntal maitilikkā vilaṅkai maṉṉaṉmuṭi yorupatumtō ḷirupatumpō yutira</l>
<l>tāṇeṭuntiṇ cilaivaḷaitta tayarataṉcē yeṉṟaṉ taṉiccaraṇvā ṉavarkkaracu karutumiṭam taṭamār</l>
<l>cēṇiṭaṅkoḷ malarkkamalam cēlkayalkaḷ vāḷai cenneloṭu maṭuttariya vutirntaceḻu muttam</l>
<l>vāṇeṭuṅkaṇ kaṭaiciyarkaḷ vārumaṇi nāṅkū rarimēya viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in lovely Arimēya Viṇṇakaram in beautiful Nānkūr where</l>
<l rend="indent">field women, with long sword[-like] eyes, when cutting fine paddy,</l>
<l>Gathering with [it] cēl, kayal and vāḷai [fish] and lotuses</l>
<l rend="indent">whose blooms attain open air [and] which fill the ponds,</l>
<l rend="indent">collect fat pearls which had dropped,</l>
<l>The place where is manifest the king of celestials, my only refuge,</l>
<l rend="indent">the son of Daśaratha who bent the long, strong bow [with his] foot,</l>
<l>So the ten crowns and twenty arms of  Lanka’s king went tumbling</l>
<l rend="indent">for the sake of Maitilī, with long lance[-like] eyes and flowery hair.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
